title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Oct 27 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Oct 27 2021
description:
GA Gov Brian Kemp on Election Law and the Braves in the World Series. Minnesota school board doxxes parents. Omar cancels cops, then blames their performance. Merrick Garland gets grilled on Capitol Hill. The guys welcome future EIB guest host Michael Berry to the show, and Jesse Kelly pops in for some laughs.
